videos.headline: Danielle Rauch buries a 3 to cut into Baylor's lead
videos.description: Emily Kiser finds an open Danielle Rauch for a 3-pointer as the Wolverines cut Baylor's lead to two points.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Danielle Rauch buries a 3 to cut into Baylor's lead) 2020/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cameron Williams' back-to-back buckets give Wolverines the lead
videos.description: Cameron Williams gets back-to-back buckets to fall as Michigan grabs the 27-25 lead over Baylor.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Cameron Williams’ back-to-back buckets give Wolverines the lead) 2020/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sarah Andrews knocks down-game tying 3 for Baylor
videos.description: Jordan Lewis gets it to Sarah Andrews for a game-tying 3-pointer for Baylor vs. Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sarah Andrews knocks down-game tying 3 for Baylor) 2020/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Emily Kiser ties it up for Michigan late in 4th
videos.description: Emily Kiser makes a nice bucket inside to tie it up with 37 seconds to go in Baylor vs. Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Emily Kiser ties it up for Michigan late in 4th) 2021/12/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Leigha Brown's big OT bucket helps Michigan take down Baylor
videos.description: Leigha Brown hits a huge layup to give Michigan its first top-5 win in program history as they defeat Baylor 74-68.
